00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:45,952
=Genius comes First=

38
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:50,440
What does

39
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:52,040
making films mean to you?

40
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:56,440
I think the most romantic thing

41
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,960
is to make our story into a film.

42
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,880
So this is your definition of romance.

43
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,160
What about you?

44
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,960
What do you think
is the most romantic thing?

45
00:02:09,640 --> 00:02:10,240
I think

46
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:15,720
it's probably when
I'm acknowledged by someone,

47
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,240
publicly confessed love,

48
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,560
and becoming the only one for him.

49
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:27,640
I am afraid I might mess it up.

50
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,160
I have realized

51
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:34,280
you are quite smart to choose me

52
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,280
the fairy costume,

53
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:37,280
but in other time, you're like a fool.

54
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,160
Fool.

55
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,640
Because you resemble a fairy.

56
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,080
Look at your big eyes,

57
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:46,760
they are spirited, cute and beautiful.

58
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,440
Then why didn't you say so
when I wore it?

59
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,280
You are already beautiful.

60
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,480
Do you need me to compliment you?

61
