Make a wish now.

63
00:03:12,115 --> 00:03:16,352
=Episode 22=
(Run! Youth)

64
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,800
Your mom is finally discharged.

65
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,160
Everything is good.

66
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:28,240
I am going to take her

67
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:31,240
out to travel the world.

68
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,240
We'll go to the Film Festival.

69
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:35,880
Come on.

70
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:36,880
What's the matter?

71
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,240
You seem lost.

72
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:40,520
Are you upset?

73
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,440
No.

74
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,720
My mom is discharged and leaving.

75
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:44,600
I'll miss her.

76
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,160
Well,

77
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,080
then we don't have to go.

78
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:50,520
Let's find a small hotel
and stay a few more days.

79
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:51,880
Dad.

80
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:54,160
Mom just got discharged.

81
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,240
Let her go home and rest.

82
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,240
Then let your dad
take you back to school.

83
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,080
No need.

84
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:01,240
You have such a long way to go.

85
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,400
Dad.

86
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,680
Don't let Mom do chores at home.

87
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,680
Take good care of her.

88
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,680
Don't do chores, Mom.

89
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,400
Don't worry.

90
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:08,520
Your dad has been
taking good care of me.

91
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,960
You are so caring towards me.

92
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,680
Come on, let me give you a kiss.

93
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:13,800
Mom, don't.

94
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,080
Be a good boy.

95
00:04:17,080 --> 00:04:18,080
Alright, enough.

96
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,440
Enough with the talking.

97
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:22,680
We'll come to support you
at the Film Festival.

98
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:24,800
We are leaving.

99
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,280
Dad.

100
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:29,720
Take care.

101
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,000
Be careful.

102
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,520
Right, listen to him.

103
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:33,800
Drive safe, okay?

104
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,960
Alright. Drive safe.

105
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:37,680
I'm going to drive at a slow pace,

106
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:40,120
ensuring the safety, okay?

107
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,240
What is it?

108
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,280
Here, something to eat.

109
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:43,800
Be a good boy.

110
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:44,840
Thank you, mom.

111
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,720
Didn't you say to drive slowly?

112
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,880
Yes, slowly.

113
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:09,120
You're going too slow.

114
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:10,840
Is that so?

115
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:13,400
At this speed, when will we get home?

116
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,680
Slow pace!

117
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,000
Just...

118
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,080
Go slow...

119
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:20,080
Safety first.

120
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:20,680
Stop it.

121
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,600
Safety.

122
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,840
Drive faster.

123
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:23,960
Faster?

124
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,120
You should've said so earlier.

125
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,560
Let's go.

126
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,080
The film is well-made.

127
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:37,800
Kang Yide

128
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:39,840
has been using your film to motivate us.

129
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:41,120
What's the use of that?

130
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,000
I can't participate either.

131
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:50,520
I have a question for you.

132
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,680
As a student of Library Management,

133
00:05:52,960 --> 00:05:54,720
why must you attend the Film Festival?

134
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,840
We are in the same class.

135
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,280
Then why do you attend it?

136
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,840
In the beginning,

137
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,400
I made the film to chase a girl.

138
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:06,840
But later, I did so
to not let down my team.

139
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,280
Now it's for making my mom happy.

140
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,280
By the way,

141
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:14,280
during the time
you and Wang Pengpeng absent,

142
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:15,280
I've thought a lot.

143
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:16,800
You did so because

144
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,280
Xiao Rang and me

145
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,840
seriously disturbed your lives.

146
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:20,960
I'm sorry.

147
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,560
It's good not living together.

148
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:25,280
However, through this Film Festival,

149
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,720
I really admire you.

150
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:29,960
Stop it.

151
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,960
I have failed,
and you are the participant.

152
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,840
I'm going to drop out.

153
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:37,840
Why?

154
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,720
I'm leaving.

155
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,280
Tell me why.

156
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,050
Thinking about the Film Festival?

157
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:15,720
Maybe we should go talk to Kang Yide.

158
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,400
Our film was shot so well.

159
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:18,720
It's qualified.

160
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:21,000
I came to him several times.

161
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:23,120
He made up excuses to send me off

162
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,080
and reject me.

163
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:26,120
Does he own this Film Festival?

164
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:27,840
Why can he decide everything?

165
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,840
In this case,

166
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:31,400
he really decides everything.

167
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,520
He made the organizing committee.

168
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:35,240
He can reject me if he wants.

169
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,720
Does President have any solution now?

170
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,400
Yu Lan said she would do something.

171
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:42,960
But before,

172
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:44,560
she had a conflict with Kang Yide.

173
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,000
I don't think there's much hope.

174
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,960
How about we go to the principal?

175
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:56,000
It's no use.

176
00:07:57,960 --> 00:07:58,840
At worst,

177
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:01,280
we just won't participate in it.

178
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:02,560
It doesn't matter.

179
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,560
We won't play with them.

180
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,840
Anyway,
no one in our team will blame you.

181
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,560
You've already done very well.

182
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:11,400
But your mom...

183
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,720
Your mom can't watch the film you shot.

184
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,960
It's okay, no worries.

185
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,560
We have worked hard together
for so long.

186
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:23,120
Forget it.

187
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:25,240
After all, we did do our best.

188
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:25,840
Right?

189
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:33,080
What's most important now
is your selection.

190
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,520
I have no mood right now

191
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:36,840
to participate in the selection.

192
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,720
Don't.

193
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,080
Let's go have midnight snack.

194
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,960
Then have a drink.

195
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:45,080
What?

196
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,400
You have
to participate in the selection.

197
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,280
In the next few days,

198
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,600
I will stay with you.

199
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:52,640
Really?

200
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,400
Really.

201
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:56,520
Then we should have a drink. Let's go.

202
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,280
What?

203
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:02,200
Take it slow.

204
00:09:04,436 --> 00:09:06,848
(Student Union Office)

205
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:08,640
President.

206
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,960
What's wrong?

207
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:12,840
I have something to tell you.

208
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,480
(Just get the award.)

209
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,720
(Why do you need to be fair?)

210
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:19,920
(This world isn't fair, anyway.)

211
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,720
(Can she, Yu Lan, do better than me?)

212
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,760
(I didn't plan to let)

213
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,280
(the person she recommended)

214
00:09:26,280 --> 00:09:27,840
(appear at the Film Festival.)

215
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:30,720
It is the evidence
of Kang Yide suspected manipulating

216
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,080
at the Film Festival,

217
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,600
and deleted Li Yanhao's film

218
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,960
maliciously.

219
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,600
Darn it.

220
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,600
President.

221
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:42,600
Did you

222
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,720
swear?

223
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,400
I have to help Li Yanhao.

224
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:52,280
This Film Festival

225
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,760
should be a fair event.

226
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:55,960
I can't let my efforts

227
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,080
be destroyed by him.

228
00:09:57,520 --> 00:09:59,400
The day after tomorrow
is the Film Festival.

229
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:00,520
There's no time left.

230
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,760
I can do it.

231
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:07,840
But I need your help.

232
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,960
Kang, why are you here?

233
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:21,480
You're still working?

234
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,720
The student union is short-staffed,

235
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,720
so I have to work more.

236
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:26,840
As the president,

237
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:27,960
you are quite competent.

238
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:30,600
The preparation for the Film Festival
is going smoothly, right?

239
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,960
Is there anything I can help with?

240
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:33,960
It is going smoothly.

241
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:41,080
I heard a girl named Zhu Ruoqing
in the Literature Department

242
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:44,080
filmed a very beautiful love story.

243
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:45,960
I like love stories,

244
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:47,160
so I look forward to it.

245
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:52,840
Zhu Ruoqing?

246
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,400
I've seen it.

247
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:56,040
It's very delicate and well-shot.

248
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:59,080
It should touch a few young girls.

249
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:01,720
I am looking forward to it.

250
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:06,160
I believe that under your leadership,
the Film Festival

251
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,720
will definitely shine.

252
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,840
Of course.

253
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:32,360
Even if we can't attend
tomorrow's Film Festival,

254
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:34,280
we must not get disheartened.

255
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:38,600
So, do you have any good ideas?

256
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,720
Share with us to lift our spirits.

257
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:43,920
I suggest we have a drink.

258
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:44,600
No.

259
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:46,480
Drinking only makes it worse.

260
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:51,840
What's with all of you?

261
00:11:52,160 --> 00:11:53,600
Looking listless.

262
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:58,400
It's just a film festival, right?

263
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,600
Look at you,

264
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,480
being so distressed.

265
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,840
At the Film Festival's opening ceremony,

266
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:08,160
our film

267
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:09,600
would have been premiered.

268
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,920
Now all the effort go in vain.

269
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:15,080
I thought it's some big deal.

270
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,160
You just want your film

271
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:17,600
to be seen by more people.

272
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,360
Indeed.

273
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:21,040
We can't even do that.

274
00:12:21,160 --> 00:12:21,960
Who said that?

275
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:23,160
From today on,

276
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,160
I allow your film

277
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:26,160
to be played in my bar

278
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:28,720
on a 24-hour continuous loop,

279
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:31,400
so everyone who comes here can see it.

280
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:34,040
If after watching, they like it

281
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:36,080
or give some review,

282
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,600
then I'll give them a half off.

283
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:38,840
Nice, huh?

284
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:39,840
That works.

285
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:43,080
Your place is too noisy
to watch the films.

286
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,760
I'm not that thoughtful.

